402f-a971-c62245ad7d55","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["One of the best features of this in-dash GPS is that it has a capacitive screen rather than resistive. This means it works like a smartphone and is more sensitive to touch input than the resistive screens found in cheaper units.","Like all the in-dash navigation units we reviewed, the 8100 NEX plays CDs and DVDs. It also has an HDMI input. This means that if you have a movie on a tablet or laptop, you can directly connect the device to the unit via an HDMI cable."]},"id":"b22e1746-1012-4eab-93a7-4680e2261762","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Help &amp; Support"},"id":"e7a39d02-ddfb-40a7-9b33-ec524882fee4","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Pioneer offers a one-year warranty, provided you purchase from an authorized dealer. It also offers email and phone support. Additionally, Pioneer has an active social media presence, which can be helpful for getting questions answered quickly. Pioneer has service centers in most major cities, so you should be able to get your unit fixed locally if you have a problem."]},"id":"880b8f65-aa4a-4076-8186-496ed6b94937","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"c0dbb122-b288-4246-a11f-0545bd466891","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["In terms of features and functionality, the Pioneer 8100 NEX is well ahead of the competition. Its inclusion of CarPlay and Android Auto give it unsurpassed smartphone integration, and its lifetime traffic and navigation services are also top of the line. It is absolutely the best in-dash navigation system on the market."]},"id":"8c97a4a4-2d53-40b0-863a-2cbc6ca6f516","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_63607","url":"/pioneer-8100-nex-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"suzanne-humphries","url":"/author/suzanne-humphries","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Suzanne Humphries","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"5Cbzn8X4VHCDchbqEBVidP","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"ter